    {
        "url": "/quotes/akiva_schaffer_522486",
        "quote": "I find that 'Ghostbusters' and 'Alien' actually have a lot in common in that they're both so naturalistic in the performances. It feels like people you could be hanging out with right now in this room, yet they're on a spaceship or killing ghosts. But the way they talk is never heightened or otherwordly.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Akiva Schaffer",
            "url": "/quotes/akiva_schaffer_522486"
        },
